title: Doctor Who - The Beginning
description:
The first three story arcs of the first season of Doctor Who, with William Hartnell.

This first Doctor lays down the foundation for the personalities of the other, later doctors; unpredictable and somewhat dark at times.

The Daleks make their first appearance here as well; this story arc would form the basis for the first Doctor Who movie starring Peter Cushing.

Transcoded with Handbrake to Apple .m4v with high bitrate. This brings the file very close to it's original ripped size.
